Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.81,0:00:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Marrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've received word that Sayid,\Nthe King of Dartania, has died,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.06,0:00:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and his son, Milza, has succeeded him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.40,0:00:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning Lord Milza has kept his vow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.86,0:00:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.16,0:00:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.51,0:02:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you predicted, Lady Zelma!\NThe Waldlind forces are on the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've already summoned Mist,\Nand hid the roads leading to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That should be good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.27,0:02:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since all we need is for Waldlind\Nto head straight for that boy's castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our job is to be Wolf Stalkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stay on their tails and\Nnever take your eyes off them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.57,0:02:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they let their guard down,\Ndon't assault them, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zeed, Flint...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:03:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From here on out, I'm counting on you\Nto look after everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.22,0:03:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.14,0:03:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be setting off in search of Dimitrie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's been seven days since my cousin breached\Nour borders by crossing the Dornir River,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but after establishing her stronghold,\Nshe hasn't budged.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what her next move might be,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I will request aid from Lord Selge\Nof Regalia, and Solon, King of Kilhis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As for Edokia, Queen of Halan,\NI'll ask for her to send the Palace of the Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding Lord Lassic,\Nwho now rules Sievis and Forbes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give him my order to invade Ozerl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.39,0:03:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Being constantly attacked has to be irritating.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give him a chance\Nto wreak as much havoc as he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What would you like to do about Theo Cornaro\Nof the Forest of Eternal Darkness?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.82,0:04:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Bultava forces\Nare heading towards Theo's castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him my order is to join the battle there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking just the cavalry for now,\Nand heading to Brother Villar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Igor, take charge of the infantry,\Nand catch up with us later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please hold a moment, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't help Lord Villar\Nwith just the cavalry in tow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be patient for now,\Nwait for Lord Solon's army,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then proceed after bolstering your forces—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never knowing what might happen\Nis what war is all about!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If anything should happen to Brother Villar,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Regalia... rather,\Nthe entire Union will be wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.49,0:04:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Full speed to Altirk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Ellet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:04:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you my brother's contracted mage?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, I am, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Selge never listens to a word I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brother is just too terrified\Nat the prospect of losing Lord Villar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.02,0:05:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Lord Selge does worship\Nthe ground Lord Villar walks on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder he can't keep his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'll make some kind of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you think so, why don't you\Ngo after him right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I think I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, if anything happens to Lord Selge,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to look for a new contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Edokia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.18,0:05:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've received a request for aid\Nfrom Lord Villar, the Earl of Altirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.39,0:05:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's asking us to send our naval forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our naval forces?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right to send the palace, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not like our navy\Nboasts any other warships...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's because we only need the one ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's just for bombarding the enemy fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Joachim?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking part as well.\NAlong with all my beloved men!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving you in charge while I'm gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading to Altirk to help Lord Villar\Nout of the dire straits he has found himself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.69,0:06:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Raise your goblets!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This ale will invigorate us on the battlefield,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and give us a pleasant rush\Nof adrenaline and courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll all be playing leading roles in this war,\Nwith zero chance you'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.12,0:06:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Solon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:07:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What if I do happen to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then you were no more than a bit player.\NSo give it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, bottoms up, men!\NThen don your masks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The role you play is that\Nof the Invincible Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No arrow on earth,\Nnor any blade shall harm you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will this battle turn out to be\Na comedy or a tragedy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let the curtain rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let the curtain rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Bultava forces are five thousand strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have a team of Artists on our side,\Nbut only two hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're recruiting soldiers from\Nthe Forest of Eternal Darkness, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:08:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how many will join.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Neither do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Holing up might be better...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.27,0:08:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can't turn this place into a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's mobilize.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Before the Bultava forces enter the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.72,0:08:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Villar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've received word that a fleet\Nis approaching from the southeastern seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A fleet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell whose fleet it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.61,0:08:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It appears to be from Dartania...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean Prince Milza\Nis coming to offer his aid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:09:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little too early for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell the admiral to be on alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.51,0:09:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Colleen...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just in case, prepare the Mirror, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.76,0:09:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U-Understood, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.52,0:09:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading down to the docks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Margaret!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So it's you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've missed you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milza has defected to the Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When his father, Sayid, protested,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,he murdered him and killed\Nevery subordinate who resisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:10:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Lord Milza has forsaken me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that cousin of mine has been waiting\Nfor Lord Milza's arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, I won't relinquish my Crest...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not without a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milza! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My father, Sayid Kuches.\NLounging complacently on a throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.65,0:10:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such a man who lacks foresight...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...has no right to a future!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you lack ambition, then be gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They've got some nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if the oars snap in two,\Nget closer to the enemy ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Dartanian ship is approaching at top speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's... Milza Kuches!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.07,0:12:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Abandon ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.87,0:12:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're deserting your own ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.87,0:12:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it means taking you with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't shed a tear over sinking this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive call.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't intend to die in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Going on the defensive to buy time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You Altirk Lords all fight the same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.07,0:13:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just as... expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The time has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our allies are retreating from the southwest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cover them by assaulting their pursuers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.27,0:13:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please, burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.88,0:13:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is now disoriented.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Surround and annihilate them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I've made it my enemy,\NAltirk is more formidable than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Back to the battlefield. Pursue the Altirk ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Villar...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Accept your fate and perish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milza, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's a man who can change\Nthe tide of war all on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I wasn't aware of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But by the same token,\Nwe only need to defeat Milza.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once he's out of the picture,\NDartania will surely ally itself with us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next time he appears on the battlefield,\Nso too shall I.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For I cannot stomach the thought of losing\Nmy valued men to Milza alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When that time comes,\Nplease allow me to accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it be ship or man,\NI shall burn it to the ground with hellfire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is Dartania not the country\Nwhere you were born?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.91,0:15:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That man annihilated my clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I am no longer a member\Nof the Mage Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.58,0:15:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am free to fight as I wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.29,0:15:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to when we left the castle,\Nwe now have twice as many soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Taking our recruiting efforts into account,\Nwho knew that we'd muster this many...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean you're\Nactually beloved, Lord Theo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, you saw it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I speak to them,\Nand it's like I don't even exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.08,0:15:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It really stung,\Nmaking me feel like an eyesore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:16:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I never paid any attention to them,\Nbut not so for Lord Theo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Perhaps simply watching over them\Nis one way to rule.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, we have\Nthe upper hand in this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haman's colossal ship, the Palace of the Sea,\Nshould be here by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Waldlind stood pat until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.73,0:16:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But all the same,\Nwe need to take every measure we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fire away, if you please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.76,0:16:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic! We won't get hit that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:16:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First volley, ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.04,0:17:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All ships, take the smaller boats ashore.\NTake as many troops and cargo as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is the Earl of Regalia! Find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did it come to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because you got ahead of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.81,0:17:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you! Get me out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I did just request backup\Nfrom Lord Solon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But we're surrounded on all sides\Nby the Waldlind forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.15,0:17:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure if they'll come or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy forces spotted!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, they really came!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,0:18:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Solon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Earl of Regalia! So glad to see you safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Solon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Get these two horses.\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.97,0:18:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as someone greatly indebted\Nto Lord Villar,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.35,0:18:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let him lose his younger brother\Nin a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, please escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Earl of Regalia has fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're currently fighting the Theater King\Nof Kilhis, who's come to his aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.49,0:18:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's a formidable opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cut off the Kilhis army's retreat.\NDefeat them no matter what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Solon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meeting the renowned Waldlind forces\Nin battle brings me the sweetest joy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I come to fight with good grace!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Surround the Kilhis forces on both sides!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Kilhis army is putting up fierce resistance,\Nand the battle is deadlocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.38,0:19:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Send in reinforcements.\NConcentrate our forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.47,0:19:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So the famed knights-at-arms\Nare joining the fray?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.22,0:19:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded on all sides.\NThere's no way to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.48,0:19:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,While I don't have the stamina to flee,\NI do have the stamina to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.77,0:19:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, huddle up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to report.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding the battle against the Kilhis forces...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.17,0:20:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was decided just a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.46,0:20:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Although our forces\Nsuffered heavy casualties...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.59,0:20:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to the efforts of the knights-at-arms,\Nthe Kilhis army has been wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.52,0:20:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are true heroes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Break from the constraints of\Nthis imperfect world...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.11,0:20:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And let us journey to an ideal world together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.53,0:20:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Word is that Solon, the King of Kilhis,\Nhas also been eliminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.24,0:20:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now, my life... comes to a close...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.01,0:21:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BLADE OF BETRAYAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.98,0:22:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Solon is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.40,0:22:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Lassic has driven\Nthe Ozerl forces to surrender,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.57,0:22:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and Lord Theo has repulsed the Bultava army.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.57,0:22:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I expected no less of Lord Lassic,\Nbut Lord Theo continues to surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.12,0:22:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How on earth did he drive back Bultava\Nwith such a small force?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.04,0:22:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are your orders for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.21,0:23:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then, let's have them invade\Ntheir respective enemy territories.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.25,0:23:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that they've lost both Ozerl\Nand Bultava as domains...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.97,0:23:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Waldlind has no other choice\Nbut to attack Altirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.84,0:23:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Their assault is sure to be fierce.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.10,0:23:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they should breach the castle gates,\Nwe have the sea on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.81,0:23:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we've got to ride out this crisis...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.04,0:23:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EPISODE 11:\NTHE FALL OF CASTLE UNICORN
